<p>more miles to Mammetz Wood camp.&nbsp;We did more training here and on April 6th we were granted a holiday, it being Good Friday.</p>
<p>April 9th I commemorated the first anniversay of leaving Sydney by writing letters.&nbsp; The following day we had more snow which lasted two days.</p>
